videos.description: Heavy underdog Rice is keeping Baylor in check so far thanks to J.T. Blasingame's interception of Seth Russell that stops another Baylor drive.
videos.headline: Baylor's offense struggling early as Russell gets picked off

videos.description: After struggling for most of the first half, Baylor finally gets into the end zone when JaMycal Hasty races in from 16 yards out to put the Bears up 7-3.
videos.headline: Baylor finally clicks on offense, takes lead on  Hasty's TD

videos.description: On fourth down and Rice in punt formation, backup QB Nate German takes the snap and rolls to the right before trying to get the punt off, but it goes off the side of his foot for a five-yard punt.
videos.headline: Rice with an epic punt failure

videos.description: Seth Russell shows off the touch with a gorgeous pass to KD Cannon in the back of the end zone for a 10-yard touchdown that increases the Baylor lead over Rice to 14-3.
videos.headline: Russell's touch pass a thing of beauty for a Baylor touchdown

videos.description: Rice ends an impressive nine-play drive with Emmanuel Esukpa's one-yard touchdown run to cut Baylor's lead to 14-10.
videos.headline: Rice punches it in to cut Baylor's lead to 14-10

videos.description: Terence Williams takes the handoff and goes right up the middle untouched for the 24-yard touchdown to boost Baylor's lead to 21-10 over Rice.
videos.headline: Williams goes untouched for 24-yard Baylor TD

videos.description: Darik Dillard run for 59 yds to the Bayl 15 Darik Dillard fumbled, forced by Tion Wright, recovered by Bayl Patrick Levels
videos.headline: D. Dillard fumbles after 59 yard run

videos.description: KD Cannon makes the catch and dashes to the end zone going up and over the defender for his second touchdown of the game to put Baylor up 38-10 on Rice.
videos.headline: KD Cannon gets flipped over for the touchdown

videos.description: Well-known for its parody-driven performances, the Rice band forms an "IX" -- for Title IX -- in reference to Baylor's sexual assault scandal.
videos.headline: Rice band marches into 'IX' versus Baylor
